# type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: TheBasics/notifications.xml:404
msgid ""
"If you want to try out a non-traditional method of notification, you might "
"want to mess around with audio alerts. If you want to have audio alerts "
"played on the monitoring server (with synthesized speech), check out <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.cstr.ed.ac.uk/projects/festival/\">Festival</ulink>. If "
"you'd rather leave the monitoring box alone and have audio alerts played on "
"another box, check out the <ulink url=\"http://radscan.com/nas.html"
"\">Network Audio System (NAS)</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://rplay.doit.org/"
"\">rplay</ulink> projects."
msgstr ""
"Si vous désirez une méthode atypique, vous pouvez essayer de vous amuser "
"avec les alertes sonores. Si vous voulez des alertes sonores sur le serveur "
"de supervision (avec voix synthéthique), essayez <ulink url=\"http://www."
"cstr.ed.ac.uk/projects/festival/\">Festival</ulink> [Anglais]. Si vous "
"voulez les recevoir sur une autre machine, testez le <ulink url=\"http://"
"radscan.com/nas.html\">Network Audio System (NAS)</ulink> (NAS) [Anglais] et "
"<ulink url=\"http://rplay.doit.org/\">rplay</ulink> [Anglais]. "
